font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >&#8226; 优化核心定位</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >将</font><font face="宋体" >“资源夜市”的“夜市”概念与核心方向深度绑定，突出“加群引荐、精准匹配、高分成”――</font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >定位为</font><font face="宋体" >“以加群引荐为起点，精准匹配资源、聚焦项目分成的资源夜市，让每一次引荐都能转化为实际收益，让每一个合作项目都能实现多方共赢”</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >，区别于普通社交平台的</font><font face="宋体" >“泛人脉”，聚焦“加群引荐落地、项目成交分成”，而非单纯的社交或会员费收益。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
