mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：完善加群运营规范和项目对接流程，搭建</font>3-5个核心行业精准社群（依托加群裂变），实现加群月活跃率≥70%，引荐裂变率≥40%，达成首批项目成交及分成落地；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >长期（</font>7-12个月）</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：达成</font>10000注册用户、20%付费会员目标，建成成熟的加群引荐体系和项目分成机制，实现加群数量≥500个，项目成交率稳步提升，形成“加群引荐-资源匹配-项目成交-分成共赢”的闭环，打造以项目分成为核心的资源匹配标杆平台。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >&#8226; 用户分层补充</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >明确</font><font face="宋体" >“用户分层”，贴合核心方向――</font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >普通会员（</font>99元）</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >聚焦</font><font face="宋体" >“加群、基础引荐、项目分成基础权益”，</font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >高级会员（</font>199元）</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >聚焦</font><font face="宋体" >“优质加群扶持、优先项目对接、更高分成比例”，兼顾不同用户的引荐和分成需求，提升客单价和用户粘性。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >二、用户加入理由与激励机制</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >用户加入的核心理由应聚焦</font><font face="宋体" >“加群引荐易落地、项目分成收益高”，摒弃泛化表述，将激励和价值具象化，重点突出“加群、引荐就能参与分成，项目成交收益远超会员费”，让用户一眼看到核心收益点。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >&#8226; 强化“加群引荐的便捷性与价值”</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >明确加群引荐是核心入口，降低用户参与门槛</font><font face="宋体" >――用户无需复杂操作，只需加入平台官方加群、行业细分加群，引荐身边有资源/需求的好友加入加群、入驻平台，即可成为引荐人，后续好友参与项目合作，即可享受分成收益，实现“加群即有机会赚分成”。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >&#8226; 细化“分成激励”的具象化（核心重点）</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >打破</font><font face="宋体" >“仅靠会员费提成”的局限，重点突出加群引荐分成和项目成交分成的高收益，用具体案例和明确分配规则强化感知，全程紧扣“加群、引荐”核心，其中</font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >加群参与项目合作的居间服务费分配原则</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >明确如下：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >加群引流激励</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：用户主动加入平台官方加群、行业细分加群，即可获得</font><font face="宋体" >“加群福利”（10元引荐抵扣券、平台资源对接优先权）；若用户主动邀请好友加群、入驻平台，可额外获得“加群引流补贴”（每成功邀请10人加群并入驻，补贴50元），降低加群、引流门槛，鼓励用户主动加群、主动引荐。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >2.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >加群引荐分成</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：用户通过加群（自己加入的加群）引荐好友成为付费会员，除原有会员提成（推荐</font>1个99元会员赚29.7元）外，额外享受“加群引荐奖励”（每个有效引荐额外奖励5-10元），加群引荐人数越多，奖励叠加越多；引荐的好友若继续引荐新用户加群、入驻，还可享受二级引荐奖励（每个有效引荐额外奖励2-3元），形成“加群-引荐-再引荐”的裂变闭环。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >3.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >项目成交分成（核心收益方向，加群参与项目合作专属分配规则）</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：用户通过加群引荐好友、参与项目合作，达成成交后，居间服务费按以下规则分配：</font> </span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 72.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Courier New';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >o<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >① 一级举荐人2人（甲方侧一级资源人、乙方侧一级居间人），共享60%居间服务费，原则上各占30%；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 72.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Courier New';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >o<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >② 二级举荐人N人，平均分配40%居间服务费；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 72.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Courier New';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >o<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >③ 引荐人身份以《举荐人链条清单》为准，确认后不得增减。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >举例说明：若项目成交产生</font>10万元居间服务费，一级举荐人2人各得3万元（共6万元），二级举荐人N人平均分配剩余4万元，收益远超会员费提成，这也是“加群、引荐”的核心吸引力。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >补充：所有加群用户、引荐人，均可享受平台免费的引荐技巧、项目对接培训，帮助用户快速掌握加群引流、高效引荐的方法，提升项目成交概率，让</font><font face="宋体" >“加群、引荐”真正转化为高收益。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >三、激励机制设计</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >激励机制需围绕</font><font face="宋体" >“加群、引荐、项目成交”展开，既要降低新手用户加群、引荐的门槛，又要鼓励用户持续活跃、主动促成项目成交，同时兼顾“新手友好”和“活跃激励”，避免用户流失，强化“坐等收益”的核心价值。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >&#8226; 优化“加群引荐任务门槛”</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >将</font><font face="宋体" >“每月推荐至少1人才能拿二级提成”调整为“新手期（前3个月）无加群引荐任务，可正常享受一级会员提成和加群引荐奖励；3个月后，每月完成1个加群有效引荐（引荐好友加群并成为付费会员），即可继续享受二级引荐奖励和项目成交二级居间收益”，降低新手用户的参与压力，先让用户“通过加群、引荐赚到第一笔钱”，建立信任，再引导其持续参与。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
