mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：新用户申请加群、注册会员时，需提交个人资料（如行业、职业、资源</font>/需求），人工审核通过后，方可加入加群、开通会员权限，避免虚假用户、违规用户加群；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >引荐审核</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：定期审核加群引荐记录，排查</font><font face="宋体" >“虚假引荐”（如同一设备注册多个账号、引荐人与被引荐人为同一人、被引荐人加群后未活跃），一经发现，扣除提成和分成、暂停引荐权限，情节严重者封号；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
