mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >项目成交审核</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：用户申请项目成交分成时，需提交项目成交证明（如签约合同、付款凭证），人工审核确认成交真实有效后，方可发放分成收益，避免虚假成交、骗取分成；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
