mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >资金审核</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：所有会员费、提成、分成提现，均需经过人工审核，确保资金来源合法，提现时需绑定本人银行卡，避免资金挪用、冒领风险。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
