mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo8;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >裂变式营销</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：以</font><font face="宋体" >“加群引荐赚分成”为核心，推出“邀请好友加群，双方各得10元优惠券（可抵扣会员费）；好友加群并成为付费会员，引荐人额外获得29.7元提成+5元加群引荐奖励”，降低用户加群、引荐门槛；同时鼓励会员分享“自身加群引荐收益案例”“项目成交分成案例”到朋友圈、行业社群，实现精准裂变，吸引更多有资源、有需求的用户加群。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
