mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >原有</font><font face="宋体" >“引入行业导师、投资人、教育平台”过于宽泛，需明确“引入标准”和“合作模式”，助力用户通过加群找到优质资源、促成项目成交：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >行业导师</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：优先引入有</font>10年以上行业经验、有优质资源、擅长项目对接的从业者（如资深投资人、成功创业者、行业专家），合作模式为“导师加入专属加群，提供付费咨询、线下分享、项目对接指导，平台抽取20%-30%服务费”，同时导师可通过加群引荐用户、促成项目成交，享受相应分成收益。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >投资人</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：引入种子轮、天使轮投资人，邀请其加入专属加群，平台为其提供优质创业项目对接（来自加群内的创业者），收取</font><font face="宋体" >“项目对接费”，同时投资人可通过加群筛选项目、达成投资合作，平台抽取少量合作服务费；投资人也可引荐优质项目入驻平台，享受加群引荐奖励和项目成交分成。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >合作伙伴</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >：优先选择与</font><font face="宋体" >“资源、创业、项目合作”相关的机构（如创业服务公司、供应链企业、知识产权机构、融资机构），合作模式为“机构入驻平台，加入专属加群，为加群用户提供专属服务（如创业指导、供应链对接、知识产权服务），平台收取入驻费+服务费分成”，丰富平台资源，提升加群用户的资源对接效率和项目成交概率。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >总结：核心优化方向</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >整体不颠覆原有</font><font face="宋体" >“会员制+推荐激励+资源匹配”的核心逻辑，重点围绕“加群引荐为起点，项目分成为核心”优化3点：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >强化差异化</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >，聚焦</font><font face="宋体" >“加群、引荐、项目分成”，明确加群参与项目合作的居间服务费分配规则，让用户快速感知“加入群，进群，这是缘分。合作项目引荐成功，坐等收益才是价值”的核心价值；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
