mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >2.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal" ><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;" ><font face="宋体" >降低加群、引荐门槛</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >，优化激励机制和会员分层，兼顾新手用户和活跃用户，让不同层级用户都能通过加群、引荐获得收益；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
